// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0936 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3440495e-5450-5b22-8570-27aa4059c69e

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
